    <p>
      The job search process takes time and a lot of hard work. Fortunately, there are 
      many ways for job seekers to go about locating employment opportunities. To 
      maximize your time and energy, utilize both online and in-person methods and be 
      purposeful in identifying opportunities that mesh with your interests, education 
