    <p>
      You’re living in the real world, but your education need not end with graduation. 
      Participate in networking opportunities and professional development opportunities 
      offered through Auburn University Alumni Association. Make work and living 
      transitions go more smoothly by understanding your pay and benefits and knowing the 
      cost of living in the city in which you’ve chosen to live. Take advantage of 
